descriptionHTML:
Vladimir Putin is the president of Russia. This digital Russia watch face with flag of Russia and president's portrait for android wear is dedicated to him.

Watch faces by YSAR Design are compatible with both round and square android wear smartwatches: Moto 360, Asus ZenWatch, LG G Watch R, LG G Watch, LG Watch Urbane, Samsung Gear Live, Sony Smartwatch 3 etc.
YSAR Design watch faces are made for most stylish smartwatch users. To get our fashionable watch face means that you have modern style and exceptional taste. Big attention was paid to modern and elegant design.

Features:
- Digital hours, minute, seconds
- Cool ambient/dim mode
- Date

Settings:
- Change the color of digits
- Background image choice


Our watch faces are available in settings right after you download from store and are simple in being set up. YSAR watch faces do not require much energy, so your smartwatch will operate for almost the same period of time as usual.
